    "rich-text-1": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Holkie</strong> is a trusted caster manufacturer and global caster supplier founded in 1995. With decades of engineering experience, patented designs, and certified production, we create caster wheels built for reliability and real-world performance.</p><p>From our China factory to our U.S., Canada, U.K., and EU warehouses, we deliver fast, flexible service to customers worldwide. As a leading Amazon seller and a dedicated caster factory, we support both small-batch orders and large B2B projects with quick shipping and professional guidance.</p><p>Whether you're looking for heavy-duty casters, furniture wheels, or custom mobility solutions, Holkie is here to help you move with confidence.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
